{"id":267640,"type":1,"name":"３１番目のお妃様","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/09/cd/267640_ZHTOe.jpg","summary":"被召选为『不走运』的王妃！？\r\n\r\n菲莉娅是位于边境中的边境的城邦领主的妹妹。\r\n突然某一天传来「菲莉娅被选为国王的王妃」的消息。\r\n不过，说是王妃，国王在三个月中只有一天的31号才会见她。\r\n谁都不放在心上的『不走运』的王妃！\r\n进入后宫的菲莉娅觉得「就这样吧、无所谓」\r\n而开始在住所的庭园里耕种…！？和麦克伦国王的恋爱何去何从！？\r\n\r\n在心机重重的后宫上演不规范的王妃努力奋斗的上位励志剧。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>第31位王妃</li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/19306\">KADOKAWA</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/10217\">B's-LOG COMIC</a>、<a href=\"/person/31312\">Flos Comic</a></li><li><span>原作: </span>桃巴(ビーズログ文庫)</li><li><span>作画: </span>七輝翼</li><li><span>人物原案: </span>山下ナナオ</li><li><span>连载开始: </span>2018-10-05(2018 Oct. Vol.69)</li>","collection":{"wish":1,"collect":2,"doing":2,"on_hold":1},"tags":[{"name":"七輝翼","count":1},{"name":"小说系列","count":1},{"name":"小说改","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":19306,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/1c/1f/19306_prsn_x413b.jpg","name":"角川","desc":"出版社"},{"id":31312,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/b7/4d/31312_prsn_CCStR.jpg","name":"Flos Comic","desc":"连载杂志"},{"id":10217,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/ac/19/10217_prsn_0kbWc.jpg","name":"B's-LOG COMIC","desc":"连载杂志"}],"relations":[{"id":247635,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/b5/02/247635_kGrr8.jpg","title":"31番目のお妃様","type":"书籍","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/247635"}],"comic":[{"id":287966,"name":"31番目のお妃様  (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/a7/68/287966_jBe99.jpg"},{"id":313059,"name":"31番目のお妃様  (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/08/1c/313059_Ba3Te.jpg"}]}